{"meta":{"title":"城东第一运动员","subtitle":"For Fun","description":"Recoding My Phd time","author":"Cheng Zhang","url":"https://coolzc.github.io","root":"/"},"pages":[{"title":"404 Not Found：该页无法显示","date":"2022-01-18T15:08:32.946Z","updated":"2022-01-18T09:25:42.930Z","comments":false,"path":"/404.html","permalink":"https://coolzc.github.io/404.html","excerpt":"","text":""},{"title":"关于","date":"2022-01-19T01:40:13.848Z","updated":"2022-01-19T01:40:13.844Z","comments":false,"path":"about/index.html","permalink":"https://coolzc.github.io/about/index.html","excerpt":"","text":"目前状态： 大龄计算机在读博士; 过往经历： 本科就读于电气工程及其自动化专业，硕士就读于电工理论新技术专业，待过国企，跳槽写过代码，虽然很菜，但是一直折腾不息; 技能库： 画过电路板，握过电烙铁，写过iOS代码，做过Nodejs后端，还有一丝丝已经遗忘的差不多了的FPGA知识; 研究方向： 半路出家研究CS，目前假装研究边缘计算，与优化算法打交道，但是并不精通，试图学习更多数学知识; Publication: A density-based offloading strategy for IoT devices in edge computing systems (link) Burst load evacuation based on dispatching and scheduling in distributed edge networks (link) Mail: coolzc@zju.edu.cn"},{"title":"书单","date":"2022-01-18T14:08:52.559Z","updated":"2022-01-18T09:25:42.931Z","comments":false,"path":"books/index.html","permalink":"https://coolzc.github.io/books/index.html","excerpt":"","text":""},{"title":"分类","date":"2022-01-18T14:08:52.577Z","updated":"2022-01-18T09:25:42.931Z","comments":false,"path":"categories/index.html","permalink":"https://coolzc.github.io/categories/index.html","excerpt":"","text":""},{"title":"友情链接","date":"2022-01-19T02:36:26.264Z","updated":"2022-01-18T09:25:42.931Z","comments":true,"path":"links/index.html","permalink":"https://coolzc.github.io/links/index.html","excerpt":"","text":""},{"title":"标签","date":"2022-01-18T14:08:52.631Z","updated":"2022-01-18T09:25:42.932Z","comments":false,"path":"tags/index.html","permalink":"https://coolzc.github.io/tags/index.html","excerpt":"","text":""},{"title":"Repositories","date":"2022-01-18T14:08:52.613Z","updated":"2022-01-18T09:25:42.931Z","comments":false,"path":"repository/index.html","permalink":"https://coolzc.github.io/repository/index.html","excerpt":"","text":""}],"posts":[{"title":"用FFD得装箱问题的非近似解","slug":"bin-packing","date":"2022-01-24T15:43:06.000Z","updated":"2022-01-24T16:04:28.370Z","comments":true,"path":"2022/01/24/bin-packing/","link":"","permalink":"https://coolzc.github.io/2022/01/24/bin-packing/","excerpt":"","text":"因为装箱问题是NP难问题,wiki中的Hardness of bin packing部分有说明。 所谓的FFD算法是指First-fit-decreasing bin packing算法。 但是尝试了很久,使用FFD的方法没有找到过反例,即非最优的解,网上搜索,大部分搜索到的是如下图的求解例子: 自己尝试了几组简单的数字组合的例子,FFD都能找到的都是最优解。 后来尝试查找wiki, 总算找到一个反例了： 当输入的items的size为44, 24, 24, 22, 21, 17, 8, 8, 6, 6. 箱子的capacity为61. 那么可以得到的解为（44，17）（24，24，8）（22，21，8，6）（6）, 而实际上，可以得到含有三个箱子的解：（44，8，8）（24，24，6，6）（22，21，17）","categories":[],"tags":[{"name":"组合优化","slug":"组合优化","permalink":"https://coolzc.github.io/tags/%E7%BB%84%E5%90%88%E4%BC%98%E5%8C%96/"}]},{"title":"杭图扫地僧","slug":"hzlib-old-man","date":"2022-01-19T01:41:40.000Z","updated":"2022-01-24T16:04:54.546Z","comments":true,"path":"2022/01/19/hzlib-old-man/","link":"","permalink":"https://coolzc.github.io/2022/01/19/hzlib-old-man/","excerpt":"","text":"杭图的人都很勤奋， 各个年龄阶段都有， 一早的自修室就已经被各路学习的人占满了座位。 这位老者坐姿很奇特， 每次都能遇见， 看看，室外高人的学习‘专座’： 年轻人们，少刷手机多看书，每天运动少躺平~","categories":[],"tags":[{"name":"个人","slug":"个人","permalink":"https://coolzc.github.io/tags/%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA/"}]},{"title":"随机过程(3)-谱分析","slug":"spectral-analysis","date":"2022-01-18T12:11:28.000Z","updated":"2022-01-24T16:05:00.395Z","comments":true,"path":"2022/01/18/spectral-analysis/","link":"","permalink":"https://coolzc.github.io/2022/01/18/spectral-analysis/","excerpt":"","text":"根据b站上的国科大张颢老师的课程板书记录，纯粹搬运，也许顺序上有根据自己的学习认知进行小小的改动。","categories":[],"tags":[{"name":"随机过程","slug":"随机过程","permalink":"https://coolzc.github.io/tags/%E9%9A%8F%E6%9C%BA%E8%BF%87%E7%A8%8B/"}]},{"title":"随机过程(2)-宽平稳过程","slug":"wss","date":"2022-01-18T12:05:17.000Z","updated":"2022-01-24T16:05:06.950Z","comments":true,"path":"2022/01/18/wss/","link":"","permalink":"https://coolzc.github.io/2022/01/18/wss/","excerpt":"","